flowchart TD
  A[Browse Catalog] --> B[View Product Details]
  B --> C[Add to Cart]
  C --> D[Review Cart]
  D -->|Remove/Update Items| D
  D --> E[Proceed to Checkout]
  E --> F[Enter Payment & Shipping Info]
  F --> G[Process Payment]
  G -->|Approved| H[Create Order]
  G -->|Declined| I[Prompt Correction: name, address, card info]
  H --> J[Order Fulfillment Begins]
  J --> K[Shipping / Confirmation Email]
